    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. It's in absolutely perfect shape\u2014basically looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, and it's been kept tucked away in the garage since day one. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next adventure. Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
