    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape, it still feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it spotless and always garaged. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I'm really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to love it just as much as I have. Come take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
